  <acronym>RAZANT</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective Non-Interventional Study to Assess Long-term Effectiveness of Zomacton速 and Factors Affecting Adherence in Patients With Growth Hormone Deficiency or Growth Retardation Due to Ullrich-Turner Syndrome</official_title>
