  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of long-term effectiveness of ZOMACTON in treatment of Growth Hormone Deficiency
      or growth retardation due to Ullrich-Turner Syndrome and assessment of compliance and
      adherence, optionally with the aid of an electronic app or patient diary.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
